Stock material: 3/8 in HDPE (or LDPE) for maximum chemical resistance.

Assembly: 
1) Stands 2x and bottom linker go together first. 
2) Slip the rounded ring body over the stands then
3) Fit in top linker. Everything should snap in place.

Features: 
Bottom linker is slightly elevated to allow for a magnetic stirrer.
Holes also allow for fluidic movement.  
Stands are solid to provide for lower center of mass, so as not to tip over.


